description: With the constant development of hardware getting better and better, the energy consumption of your computer rises because you want to get the full performance. Due to this the heat increases and so the requirements of your fan rise as well. To integrate several fans is not the right solution because your computer will get very, very noisy. Bigger fans are the optimal solution for modern high-tech systems. The MegaFlow fan has a diameter of 200mm and so it has a displacement volume of 184 m3/h - twice the volume of 140mm fans.700RPM 110 CFM High air flow for maximum cooling performance.Quiet operation with low RPM.RoHS compliance for protecting the environment.Compatible with 230mm HAF mounts for easy upgrades.Cosmos SHAF 932HAF 922ATCS 840CM Storm SniperRecommended as a replacement or additional fan for:HAF 932, HAF 922*, COSMOS S, ATCS 840, CM Storm Sniper**Fan and LED will operate but full LED ON/OFF function will not be compatibleModelR4-LUS-07AB-GPDimension200 x 200 x 30 mmSpeed (R.P.M.)700 RPMAir Flow (CFM)110 CFMAir pressure (mmH2O)0.595 mm H2ONoise Level19 dBABearing TypeSleeve BearingFan Life Expectancy30,000 hrsRated Voltage12 VDCCurrent (Ampere)0.16 A (Max 0.28 A)Power consumption3.36 WWeight266 g; 0.59 lbConnector3 Pin3 to 4 pin Adapter1 pcsColorBlue LEDScrews4 pcsUPC Code884102004018
